<subSubSection id="09AB84DA4214894CFF755FD4FD7DC516" pageId="19" pageNumber="29" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="410ED7514214894CFF755FD4FE98C4F9" blockId="19.[227,348,1179,1205]" box="[227,348,1179,1205]" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">
<heading id="1A46603D4214894CFF755FD4FE98C4F9" bold="true" box="[227,348,1179,1205]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="19" pageNumber="29" reason="3">
<emphasis id="73C50B434214894CFF755FD4FE98C4F9" bold="true" box="[227,348,1179,1205]" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="410ED7514214894CFF755F82FD7DC516" blockId="19.[225,1437,1228,1376]" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">
Genus of the family 
<taxonomicName id="86B1ACD24214894CFE5D5F83FD97C4AA" authorityName="Korn" authorityYear="2001" box="[459,595,1228,1254]" class="Cephalopoda" family="Taouzitidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ammonoidea" pageId="19" pageNumber="29" phylum="Mollusca" rank="family">Taouzitidae</taxonomicName>
with extremely discoidal, subinvolute to involute conch; venter subacute or acute in the adult stage. With single ventrolateral grooves. Suture line with wide external lobe, high median saddle, V-shaped E2 lobe, V-shaped lateral lobe and shallow, rounded umbilical lobes. Suture line formula (E 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFE005E1DFE5BC52C" attach="left" box="[406,415,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">2</subScript>
E 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFE2E5E1DFE05C52C" attach="left" box="[440,449,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">1</subScript>
E 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFE4C5E1DFE27C52C" attach="left" box="[474,483,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">2</subScript>
) L U 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFDB75E1DFDEEC52C" attach="left" box="[545,554,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">2</subScript>
U 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFDD05E1DFD8BC52C" attach="left" box="[582,591,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">4</subScript>
: U 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFDE55E1DFDB8C52C" attach="left" box="[627,636,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">3</subScript>
U 
<subScript id="DD35D5144214894CFD0E5E1DFD65C52C" attach="left" box="[664,673,1362,1376]" fontSize="6" pageId="19" pageNumber="29">1</subScript>
I.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
